'''Wa no Mutsu Agata''' (倭の六県, also known as '''Roku no Miagata''') refers to six directly governed territories of the {{ill|Great King|ja|治天下大王|qq=draft|qq=draft}} (imperial family) in ancient {{ill|Yamato Province|ja|Yamato Province|qq=draft|qq=draft}}.

