* '''Katsuragi County''' (葛城県) - {{ill|Katsujō District|ja|葛上郡|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Katsuge District|ja|葛下郡|qq=draft|qq=draft}}

Within these areas, several shrines bearing the name of their respective counties were established as {{ill|Shikinai shrines|ja|式内社|1=Shikinaisha|2=ja|3=式内社|qq=draft|1=Shikinaisha|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, including:
